    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1888-03-19">9 P M March 19</date>
                    <date when="1888-03-19">'88<ptr target="loc.07636_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute/>
            </opener>

            <p>I was out yesterday to my friends the Harneds<ptr target="n4146"/>, &#38; took a 3 or 4 mile drive
                afterward at sunset. The weather is pleasent&#8212;seems settled&#8212;I still write
                bits for the H[erald]<ptr target="n4133"/>&#8212;Haywood<ptr target="nyp.00450_n2"/> the Mass: free lover here to-day, very cordial &#38;c. I
                treat him politely but that is all.<ptr target="loc.07636_n2"/>  I rec'd yrs: with L[ippincott]'s
                declination<ptr target="loc.07636_n3"/>&#8212;Eakin[s]<ptr target="n3166"/> has taken away his picture &#38; I havn't seen him for
                ten days<ptr target="loc.07636_n4"/></p>
            
            <closer>
                <salute/>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
